Ottawa DogWatch - Providing safe, secure, electronic hidden dog fences, pet containment systems, and pet friendly training products to the Ottawa and Eastern Ontario area.

Our electronic hidden wire fences work indoors and out for both dogs and cats featuring a pet-friendly FM radio signal, life-time equipment warranty, and the longest battery life in the industry.
